user.biography:
Premium baby necessities made for modern mamas
Organic cotton + buttery soft knit fabrics
swaddles, bibs, 3-layer quilts, gowns, headbands
& more 🤍

node.text:
Please watch and send some ❤️ as we share our story about Jane ❄️

A portion of all our Jane proceeds will be donated to The March of Dimes - which leads the fight for the health of all mothers and babies ❤️

node.text:
It’s AUSSIE time mate! This new collection is one we’ve been so excited to share with you!! We’re so grateful to have Copper Pearl in Australia and we wanted to show our support to all our Aussie friends with this new print! 

Check out the video above and let us know if you have any questions 👇🏼 we hope you ❤️ it as much as we do!

"DO YOU KNOW EXACTLY WHAT TO DO IF A BABY CHOKES?

These 30 seconds could save a life!

Tag a mama or expectant mother who needs to see this! ☀️"

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Copper Pearl | Modern Baby on July 28, 2021.

node.text:
MESA is here! The cutest faded clay color (think terra-cotta style)! We asked you about this quilt a LONG time ago and it’s finally here! We made sure to bring it in all the things so there was something for everyone 🤍 The full collection is on our site now + a few things in our Amazon storefront. You can also shop local by finding a store near you, just click the store locator tab at the bottom of our website 🙌🏼
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Tag a mama who’d love this print and let us know if you have any questions below 👇🏼

node.text:
📣 Calling all mamas! We’ve got a new mom hack for you🚨

We’re a team full of moms over here at Copper Pearl HQ and we want to share some of our favorite mom hacks!

This $10 laundry tote is the most versatile bag you’ll ever own! It’s collapsible, light weight, and cute! We use it as a catch all bag for the car, grocery bag tote, and a pool bag! We’re sure there a dozen other ways this thing could come in handy, don’t you think?! 🙌🏼

#momhacks

node.text:
RUN! We just dropped 26 sleep bags into our SALE section on our website 🏃🏻‍♀️ Prices as low as $32! If you’ve been wanting to try one of our 3 layer, buttery soft, ultra cozy sleep bags now is the time! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
About our sleep bags ⬇️
• they have a TOG rating of 1.25. This means the sleep bags are ideal for home temperatures between 65-75° F
• they have a top to bottom zipper for both safety and convenience
• we currently have two sizes: 0-6 months and 6-12 months
